flowchart LR
    APP[Applications] --> SCAN[SCAN / Services]
    SCAN --> DB1[DB Node 1]
    SCAN --> DB2[DB Node 2]
    DB1 <--> GI[Grid Infrastructure / ASM]
    DB2 <--> GI
    DB1 <--> FABRIC[RoCE ou InfiniBand Fabric]
    DB2 <--> FABRIC
    FABRIC <--> CELL1[Storage Cell 1]
    FABRIC <--> CELL2[Storage Cell 2]
    FABRIC <--> CELL3[Storage Cell 3]
    CELL1 --> GD1[Grid Disks]
    CELL2 --> GD2[Grid Disks]
    CELL3 --> GD3[Grid Disks]
    GD1 --> ASM[ASM Diskgroups]
    GD2 --> ASM
    GD3 --> ASM
